	Cadence de Tir Améliorée
	"

3667, "(fr)A Vasudan variant of the Subach HL-7 design with enhanced rate of fire and range, at the cost of per-shot damage. This design met Vasudan requirements for better long-range attack during the Second Shivan Incursion, but the Balor cannon rendered it obsolete.
"

3668, "
	Perturbateur de Sous-Système
