7063, "(fr)Keep your PDS at the ready, Gloire. There's a lot of them and we're liable to let a few leak."

7064, "(fr)We lost the Gloire and the boarding party! Op's a wash, people. Let's get our people off the Agincourt, blow the ship, and get out."

7065, "(fr)Tev fire has saturated our point defenses and passed our safe armor threshold. We're on the red-line now pilots."

