7274, "(fr)We just lost the Dea Bricta!"

7275, "(fr)This is your aristeia, Noemi. Fight, and you will triumph."

7276, "(fr)I don't think we want to keep him waiting. Banzai that AWACS, Wargods! Watch the escorts!"

