7278, "(fr)Affirmative. All torpedo stations, get me salvo fire on the Hood. Show them out."

7279, "(fr)Gunnery, target the Hood's main beam emitter with the CG-4s."

7280, "(fr)Run home, little Tev. Tell Steele I'm coming for him."

